{"tid":1222913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連因航都正名了","createTime":"2019-06-14T14:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T15:42:28.000Z","uid":228995,"like":104,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7707124065b27496824e21efeb4828a5f3297a23","tid":1222913,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:44:06.000Z","msg":"//【 #絕不腳軟 揮手區 】<br />\n<br />\n#有種旅人 一向不怕行街，甚至用雙腳四圍探索也絕不腳軟。<br />\n確實，#路是人行出來的！只要有夥伴同行，十分鐘、半小時，甚至幾小時也不覺得孤單，終點更比想像中近！你下次會 #由家出發 到哪裡，用雙腳征服最美風景呢？<br />\n<br />\n #仍然要相信這裡會有想像 #一同起步<br />\n<br />\n#Hongkongers are keen explorers, which is why some of us prefer to get around on foot. After all, paths are made by walking &mdash; as long as you&rsquo;ve got the right company, it doesn&rsquo;t matter if the journey takes ten minutes, 30 minutes, or even hours. Which destination will you conquer next?//<br />\n<br />\n繼教師、逗號、基督徒、00後、港女，<br />\n又一大軍加入！"},{"pid":"f3e584d92cc90a55249894e292c946e0cd2af209","tid":1222913,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:46:10.000Z","msg":"Link ?"},{"pid":"f1d82a4a8359a7c4567c1ba53f215aeef900607d","tid":1222913,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:53:12.000Z","msg":"【輿論組請注意】有關張貼任何消息之事宜<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1221175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1221175</a>"},{"pid":"c789be39b98bf371e5586d4aa16f8b7bb8f718cf","tid":1222913,"uid":228995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f3e584d92cc90a55249894e292c946e0cd2af209","tid":1222913,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:46:10.000Z","msg":"Link ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:55:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/328735300603513/posts/1680344665442563?s=530560379&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F328735300603513%2Fposts%2F1680344665442563%3Fs%3D530560379%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Q%2Bw